  "remarks": "T-Bank is one of the three largest banks in Russia, based on the number of its active clients. It holds a leading position in the field of financial technologies, and the Central Bank of Russia has included Tinkoff Bank on the list of systemically-important credit institutions. T-Bank was known as Tinkoff Bank until 5 June 2024.",
